{"word":"ὠφελητέος","slug":"ὠφελητέος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὠφελητέος</b></el> <el>(ὠφελητέος, η, ον,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:verbal Adjective'>verb. <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a></a> of <a href='S:ὠφελέω'><el>ὠφελέω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>necessary</i> or <i>proper to be assisted</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><el>ὠφελητέον</el>, <i>one must assist</i>, <el>τὴν πόλιν</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}